    Here are some facet's of other MH environments:


				   Mail

    To make a .mailrc file from an MH aliases file, use the
    make_mailrc.sh script.  See make_mailrc.doc for the details.
    (John A. Dilley <terrapin@purdue>)


			      Append Editor

    append.sh has an editor that can be used at What Now? level.
    See append.rf for the details.  (Bob Desinger <hpda!bd@berkeley>)

    amhmail.sh is like mhmail but expands aliases (Andy Crump <andyc@inteloc>)
